                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>to obtain the situation of another especially when he has a position which<lb/>\n                secures him a living. But as you do not ask my opinion to govern you<lb/> in your\n                choice, I have to repeat that I <del>?</del> refer you to those<lb/> having the\n                information desired to enable you to come to a correct<lb/> judgment.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">It is my sincere hope that you may resolve<lb/> on the best method\n                to promote the interest of our Religion, and<lb/> that peace &amp; good will may\n                reside among you. I need not add<lb/> that I shall be happy to be of any service in\n                my power to your<lb/> congregation &amp; you individually for the kind consideration\n                manifested<lb/> towards me and my public labours.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Wishing you <add>Hebrew</add> and that your prayers may<lb/> be\n                answered.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">I am</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">Resp your obt servt</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Isaac Leeser</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
